.Ve
.SS "to_datetime"
.IX Subsection "to_datetime"
.Vb 1
\&  my $str = $date\->to_datetime;
.Ve
.PP
Render \s-1RFC\s0 3339 <http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc3339> date and time.
.PP
.Vb 2
